1319 private static SoundStyle CreateTrackable(string name, int variations, SoundType type = SoundType.Sound)
1320 {
1321 if (_trackableLegacySoundPathList == null)
1322 {
1323 _trackableLegacySoundPathList = new List<string>();
1324 }
1325 _ = _trackableLegacySoundPathList.Count;
1326 if (variations == 1)
1327 {
1328 _trackableLegacySoundPathList.Add(name);
1329 }
1330 else
1331 {
1332 for (int i = 0; i < variations; i++)
1333 {
1334 _trackableLegacySoundPathList.Add(name + "_" + i);
1335 }
1336 }
1337 return new SoundStyle("Terraria/Sounds/Custom/" + name + ((variations > 1) ? "_" : null), 0, variations, type);
1338 }

1340 public static void FillAccessMap()
1341 {
1342 Dictionary<string, SoundStyle> ret = new Dictionary<string, SoundStyle>();
1343 Dictionary<string, ushort> ret2 = new Dictionary<string, ushort>();
1344 Dictionary<ushort, SoundStyle> ret3 = new Dictionary<ushort, SoundStyle>();
1345 ushort nextIndex = 0;
1346 List<FieldInfo> list = (from f in typeof(SoundID).GetFields(BindingFlags.Static | BindingFlags.Public)
1347 where f.FieldType == typeof(SoundStyle)
1348 select f).ToList();
1349 list.Sort((FieldInfo a, FieldInfo b) => string.Compare(a.Name, b.Name));
1350 list.ForEach(delegate(FieldInfo field)
1351 {
1352 ret[field.Name] = (SoundStyle)field.GetValue(null);
1353 ret2[field.Name] = nextIndex;
1354 ret3[nextIndex] = (SoundStyle)field.GetValue(null);
1355 nextIndex++;
1356 });
1357 SoundByName = ret;
1358 IndexByName = ret2;
1359 SoundByIndex = ret3;
1360 }
